'''Abeiku Nana Acquah''' yɛ Ghanani siniyifo a edin a wɔde nim paa ne ‘’Killer’’, a ɛyɛ edin a ɔde dii dwuma wɔ sini bi ɛbɛyɛɛ TV so dwumadie w’ato din ''Things We Do For Life''. W’ayɛ sini ahodoɔ pii wo [[Ghana]] a emu bi ne Scent of ''Dange''r ne ''A Stinge In A Tail''

== Nnwuma ==
Abeiku Nana Acquah ka TV so dwumadie sini a w’at din ''Police Officer'' ne ''Things We Do For Love.''Abeiku Nana Acquah hyee sisniyi ase bre a na osua a w’adi mfie dunsian (16) na wɔka ne ho asɛm sɛ Ghana siniyifo a w’akye wo siniyi mu.

